{"tid":617971,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［黑店］罷買樂高寵物店 LEGO PET 全線分店","createTime":"2018-04-05T12:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T05:30:51.000Z","uid":124526,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd41d6e68c4c8838ae6a0968ab88f78c6b5b81d","tid":617971,"uid":124526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:31:56.000Z","msg":"打盲隻狗當無事，我以後唔L會幫襯。"},{"pid":"3df5696ca10e79ee7de39aa401eb92d522efeaba","tid":617971,"uid":124526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"【狗狗極悲】波波到荃灣寵物店沖涼後，冇咗隻眼&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180402/2_579529_0/-狗狗極悲-波波到荃灣寵物店沖涼後-冇咗隻眼-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F2_579529_0%2F-%E7%8B%97%E7%8B%97%E6%A5%B5%E6%82%B2-%E6%B3%A2%E6%B3%A2%E5%88%B0%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9%E5%BA%97%E6%B2%96%E6%B6%BC%E5%BE%8C-%E5%86%87%E5%92%97%E9%9A%BB%E7%9C%BC-&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=92fd10e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F2_579529_0%2F-%E7%8B%97%E7%8B%97%E6%A5%B5%E6%82%B2-%E6%B3%A2%E6%B3%A2%E5%88%B0%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9%E5%BA%97%E6%B2%96%E6%B6%BC%E5%BE%8C-%E5%86%87%E5%92%97%E9%9A%BB%E7%9C%BC-&h=e64c5c3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180402/2_579529_0/-狗狗極悲-波波到荃灣寵物店沖涼後-冇咗隻眼-</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/204549_4cf52531fa1c0a97ea168037075e6147.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F204549_4cf52531fa1c0a97ea168037075e6147.png&h=f0784c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前記者到在facebook得悉一單狗界悲劇，Suki（化名） 在社交網站表示，「波波到荃灣一間寵物店沖涼後，冇咗隻眼&hellip;&hellip;」 <br />\n<br />\n記者立即聯絡事主了解事件來龍去脈，她表示上月中帶松鼠狗波波到荃灣大壩街一間寵物美容店沖涼，約一小時後接到店員電話，指指波波沖涼期間「爆眼瘡」，着她帶走波波去看醫生。 <br />\n<br />\nSuki到達寵物美容店後，驚見波波右眼出血，眼球幾乎跌出來，她二話不說立即愛犬到附近獸醫診所求醫，經醫生進行眼皮縫合手術後，證實波波右眼視網膜脫落，永久失明，但獸醫表盲眼與「爆眼瘡」完全無關 。 <br />\n<br />\n由於事態嚴重，Suki 致電美容院追究，希望了解出事原因，女職員卻堅稱：「波波沖涼期間完全無掙扎，一直很乖，所以不知道事情怎樣發生。」Suki 再翻看寵物美容店提供的閉路電視錄影，由於角度有盲點，亦追查不到事發經過及原因。 <br />\n<br />\n經過一番周旋，寵物美容店最後僅願意負責一萬元作賠償，對此 Suki 向記者表示：「無可能隻狗沖沖下涼可以盲咗隻眼，就算寵物店賠償一萬蚊比我，又有乜用？」"},{"pid":"e835f6cfeaec083490dbaa11d4d89f122a71d89b","tid":617971,"uid":39600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4bd41d6e68c4c8838ae6a0968ab88f78c6b5b81d","tid":617971,"uid":124526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:31:56.000Z","msg":"打盲隻狗當無事，我以後唔L會幫襯。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"未必係打既 可能唔夠小心撞到隻眼<br />\n不過寵物呢行係有啲人渣既"},{"pid":"96eeba0f047cf4ba06aede9865d52ad3e1aaa489","tid":617971,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f0285d789a2c9c3e7bd63b342ed73a89d88043","tid":617971,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T23:39:24.000Z","msg":"Good job"},{"pid":"3438c5febc7e796cb88dfdc807b643d7ae3d6485","tid":617971,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"狗狗好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知做d幫可以整執間鋪唔好再害人<br />\n不過動物係連燈睇黎賤過地底泥<br />\n隔離po有人比人影相放上網幾個鐘就推到開新po （我唔係話影人係啱，只係覺得對比好大）<br />\n隻狗狗比人攪到隻眼冇埋都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f553ca33eb3ca95271179e493c959171592316ae","tid":617971,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:24:32.000Z","msg":"睇原圖狗狗隻眼跌出黎口咁濟爆眼瘡都講得出<br />\n真係想睇佢地爆瘡係點"},{"pid":"830367fe0ec84be831cf0ca9f5ee485b2399b707","tid":617971,"uid":25061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"到底要幾大力撞會撞到隻眼無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b85d59b86dcb8928dd2ba72e1f315fe21b807de","tid":617971,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隻貓之前都去過lego pet度沖涼<br />\n好彩我全程係玻璃門望到實<br />\n個店員好彩都冇打我隻貓<br />\n不過如果自己沖到就自己沖啦<br />\n見隔離d狗又腳震又想走<br />\n試過依次而家我都係自己沖算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/084641_c4eb3ee3585d18a660d247ef81b29b8e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F084641_c4eb3ee3585d18a660d247ef81b29b8e.png&h=09c816cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/084644_b8a248c5622650beb73e702b0f1b68e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F084644_b8a248c5622650beb73e702b0f1b68e9.png&h=fdb8eaac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/084645_8a426abe1b4597a61f078e93c58e7026.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F084645_8a426abe1b4597a61f078e93c58e7026.png&h=c16085ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c210b650839cd56226521cbbbfdbeae1abbc3b1c","tid":617971,"uid":72952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T02:55:45.000Z","msg":"以前帶貓去PET SHOP沖涼(唔同舖)<br />\n一次染耳虱, 一次金錢癣<br />\n以後唔會帶去寵物店<br />\n搵人上門沖<br />\n一來乾淨<br />\n二來全屋人睇實,唔會有咩事發生"},{"pid":"ec9c1ff84386120c7295cdaa2caac3529abed626","tid":617971,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c210b650839cd56226521cbbbfdbeae1abbc3b1c","tid":617971,"uid":72952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T02:55:45.000Z","msg":"以前帶貓去PET SHOP沖涼(唔